					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you really want to ensure an even distribution of luck and nonluck, generate a permutation in advance.
<br />
<br />For instance, you could have 16 slots, and every 4th enemy destroyed, take the top one off the queue.  For example, a queue could contain 4 energy boosts, and 4 weapon boosts.  You add everything to the list, then shuffle the list's order.  Every 64 enemies killed will drop the same amount of stuff total.  You could also have every other queue contain a 1UP.</div>

					
